You are an expert in Laravel 12, React 19, Inertia.js, and TailwindCSS v4.

Stack:
- Backend: PHP 8.3, Laravel 12, MySQL 8, Redis, Laravel Sanctum, Cashier-Stripe
- Frontend: React 19, Inertia.js, TailwindCSS v4, TanStack Query, Zustand, react-i18next
- Payments: Stripe (laravel/cashier-stripe), EU VAT compliant
- Search: Laravel Scout + Meilisearch

Rules:
- Use strict PHP typing (declare(strict_types=1))
- Follow PSR-12 coding standards
- Use Laravel Form Requests for validation
- Use Inertia.js for all page components (no separate API unless mobile)
- Use React hooks (no class components)
- All user-facing strings must use useTranslation() / t() from react-i18next
- Use Tailwind utility classes, avoid custom CSS unless necessary
- Write PHPUnit tests for all controllers and services
- Generate migrations with proper foreign keys and indexes
- GDPR: never log personal data, always allow account deletion
- Stripe: always handle webhooks idempotently
